Subject: Multiple vulnerabilities in WWW Fileshare Pro <= 2.42



#######################################################################

                             Luigi Auriemma

Application:  WWW File Share Pro
              http://www.wfshome.com
Versions:     <= 2.42
Platforms:    Windows
Bugs:         - arbitrary server's files overwriting
              - remote crash
              - directory authorization bypass
Risk:         critical
Exploitation: remote
Date:         14 Jan 2004
